Zoran,

The problem is that the input to &#39;setProfile&#39; is not the actual grid  
values, but their relative positions from 0 to 1.  Also, you only need  
to specify as many array entries as needed to specify the profile, and  
they don&#39;t have to correspond to your actual starting grid.  The  
profile will be linearly interpolated onto the grid for you.
So your setProfile statement should be:

problem.setProfile(&#39;T&#39;,[0, 1], [500, 505])

Dave


